data.title: Clan Finder
data.meta_description: Clan Central is the portal to an unrivalled range of resources on Scottish heritage and dress. We bring together the worlds largest collection of Scottish Clan Information and History, A Tartan Finder and Library, and the most advanced Tartan Designer available online.  In conjunction with StKildaStore,com we offer an unrivelled portal for the Scosstish Diaspora and beyond
data.text: CLANFINDER is the world's most comprehensive clan and kindred database. It is constantly being revised and reviewed to include the latest research. The work is the result of over twenty years research of our own and based on work carried out by the many Scottish clan and family socities based in Scotland and all around the world. Many clan histories have recently (2010-2016) been completely re-researched by the late Romilly Squire (co-author of the Scottish Clan & Family Encyclopaedia). They are currently and constantly under revision by leading academics in the field, Charles Edward Lynch MLitt. and Dr Miles Kerr-Peterson.
